         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">10/5/92. ¶  ¶ This time, esteemed Dr Nordstedt, I am just writing to report that I have gained about six subscriptions for the Characeae. ¶  ¶ Mr. C. French, Melbourne,  ¶  ¶ Mr. G. Luehmann, " ¶  ¶ M...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">92.05.10a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">To Otto Nordstedt</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">Handskr. avdl., Universitetsbibliotek, Lund.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">10/5/92.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Diesmal, geehrter Herr Dr. Nordstedt, schreibe ich nur, um zu melden, dass ich etwa 6 Subscriptionen für die Characeen gewonnen habe.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               </seg>Mr. C. French, Melbourne, </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. G. Luehmann, "</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. O Tepper, Adelaide,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. J.H. Maiden, Sydney</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <seg style="">Ich selbst nehme auch ein Ex.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich werde fortfahren, Subscriptionen zu suchen, und Ihnen das Resultat von Zeit zu Zeit mittheilen. So wird wohl die Fortsetzung Ihres wichtigen Werkes innerhalb </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">wirklich spezifischer</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Grenzen zu sichern sein.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Sie ehrend</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Grüssen Sie den edlen und venerablen Agardh bestens von mir.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">10/5/92.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>This time, esteemed Dr Nordstedt, I am just writing to report that I have gained about six subscriptions for the Characeae.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">The proposed continuation of Nordstedt (1891).</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. C. French, Melbourne, </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. G. Luehmann, "</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. O Tepper, Adelaide,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr. J.H. Maiden, Sydney</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will also take a copy myself</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I will continue to seek subscriptions and inform you of the results from time to time. So the continuation of your important work will probably be assured within <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">really specific</hi>
               </seg> boundaries.<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg style="">Despite M's hopes, no further D</seg>
                     <seg style="">ecades were published after he was unable to continue subsidizing the production; see M to O. Nordstedt, 31 January 1892 (in this edition as 92-01-31a).</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Best greetings to the noble and venerable Agardh from me.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
